{"tid":2452162,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"57歲烏鴉張耀揚肌肉綻爆恤衫 攬中女唱《誰令你心痴》再騷歌喉","createTime":"2021-03-18T15:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:52:03.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51dbf915fc28eec4efb5bcd96680f7e84bb79449","tid":2452162,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"現年57歲嘅張耀揚曾喺電影系列《古惑仔》中扮演烏鴉同東星耀揚，霸氣「大佬」形象深入民心。早年佢已經離開娛樂圈轉戰澳門發展賭業，並經常行善，舊年8月佢就同莫少聰、林國斌、張敏等人去到青藏高原嘅青海玉樹，到貧困村落扶貧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2910000/2910272/73fd2290-be83-497e-8c21-7855103b42b4_600_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2910000%2F2910272%2F73fd2290-be83-497e-8c21-7855103b42b4_600_600.jpg&h=7e3fb1c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd9f9453c2f9375e8d351564d836f76f614fc9d1","tid":2452162,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzeJY6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzeJY6b.jpg&h=1802f3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2280000/2281023/TUNGSTAR727717_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2280000%2F2281023%2FTUNGSTAR727717_600.jpg&h=d0cd738b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"058940bdee00e2726307f07f970cbb052d396d42","tid":2452162,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"日前，張耀揚再有一輯近照。身穿深藍色條紋西裝背心嘅佢渾身肌肉，幾乎將背心裏面嘅恤衫逼爆。佢亦無懼一頭銀髮顯老，由得佢自然生長，束起一條小馬尾，佬味爆燈！之後流出佢同一名女士合唱嘅片段，原來係耀揚早幾日出席好朋友飯局「上海灘之夜」，興之所至大展歌喉。<br />\n<br />\n雖然未知佢有冇再獻唱《愛我別走》，但張耀揚左手搭住一名中女，合唱《誰令你心痴》，可惜片段啱啱錄唔到張耀揚獻唱，但都見到佢跟住音樂打拍子搖擺身體，睇嚟相當享受。"},{"pid":"6b9f5a75c0bffcc125b45a589fc2e2192cb8b7cb","tid":2452162,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjGz5Mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjGz5Mg.jpg&h=cdef41a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18cad473617646c7fbc7cf32764caf34963fc330","tid":2452162,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:53:24.000Z","msg":"雖然已經冇再喺娛圈打滾，但張耀揚一啲都冇「鬆懈」，仍然keep住當年拍電影時嘅身形，甚至係有過之而無不及！上年9月佢就俾朋友「出賣」post出一張佢食住雪茄玩電話嘅型仔相，相中嘅佢戴住黑超chok爆，網民都大讚佢型到核爆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQnjxrm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQnjxrm.jpg&h=5d5630f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3763e5878a5ab016890bc8d02c97b7d242f10078","tid":2452162,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"又回帶.."},{"pid":"f3c05400d4df5db7f975be25e751188c84307ca8","tid":2452162,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3763e5878a5ab016890bc8d02c97b7d242f10078","tid":2452162,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"又回帶.."},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"唉真係 我助手手多多㩒發文  已經叫停佢點知佢手快得濟貼左過時文<span class=\"x-large\"> 😌<br />\n</span> very pardon <span class=\"x-large\"> 😌<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a9ee6d63c82d98d66cda32b47f9e4e1eebf795b6","tid":2452162,"uid":3962,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T18:05:48.000Z","msg":"係佢令到我細個飲茶成日驚俾人反枱"},{"pid":"16af02ee1f27a5cf942356f96694448101af7dc1","tid":2452162,"uid":259639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T18:30:06.000Z","msg":"好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b634e7b510628232202032eb47ba82aef6d159","tid":2452162,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3c05400d4df5db7f975be25e751188c84307ca8","tid":2452162,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3763e5878a5ab016890b